nodes.text: Nameel was a forested world inhabited by a Trandoshan tribe led by Warlord Vurrsk, as well as Dupei monks. The Dupei stole credits from the Trandoshans, and when they retaliated, the Jedi Eno Cordova and Cere Junda were sent to restore the peace. Junda mistakenly aggravated the Trandoshans, assuming they were at fault, but Cordova discovered the monks' theft.
